I will not sign anything yet because I will not normalize withholding information which I view as a violation of patient autonomy because I refuse to let us create a situation where patients participate in research without knowing they may not receive active treatment because I hold their right informed consent sacred which I must protect because I owe them honesty about all trial aspects including placebos which I consider essential to their ability to make truly informed decisions which I deeply respect because their autonomy matters more than our convenience which I acknowledge because I understand we both face pressure to complete trials quickly which I recognize but I also know we

